    "synopsis": "When the Catachan 183rd is stranded in the lethal jungles of Pythos, a plague of daemons descends from the skies and the Warmaster Abaddon himself leads the assault. With the Death Guard and Black Legion arrayed against them, the Guardsmen seem doomed — until the entire Dark Angels Chapter arrives under Supreme Grand Master Azrael. But the Dark Angels have their own reasons for coming to Pythos, and the daemon-hunting Grey Knights of Grand Master Draigo are drawn by the mystery of the Damnation Cache buried beneath the world. From desperate ground fighting to a void battle and a final confrontation deep below the surface, the fate of Pythos turns on the secret the Cache holds.",
